# gotiengviet-js

TypeScript library adding Vietnamese typing (Telex, VNI, VIQR) to web apps. Zero runtime dependencies.

## Key constraints

- Public API only via `src/index.ts`: `VietnameseInput`, `InputConfig`, `InputMethod`
- Singleton pattern: `getInstance()` / `destroyInstance()`
- No new runtime dependencies
- Docs live in `docs/` (Vietnamese); update there, not root README

## Commands

```bash
npm run build   # Rollup → dist/
npm test        # Jest + jsdom
npm run lint    # ESLint
npm run format  # Prettier
```

## Feature task workflow

Orchestrator: `implement-feature-task`. Phase skills: `receive-feature-requirement` → `analyze-feature-tasks` → `track-feature-tasks` → `implement-feature-code` → `run-quality-gate` → `sync-feature-docs` → `gitflow-feature-merge`.

- No PR; merge `feature/*` → `develop` with `--no-ff`
